<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head') %></head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 flex flex-col">
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="hero-grad">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28 text-center text-white">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-indigo-100 border border-white/15 text-xs font-medium">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span>
          AI-augmented peer review - running offline by default
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-6 leading-tight">
          Submit, match, review, publish <span class="text-indigo-200">with AI in the loop.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-slate-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          A modern paper submission and peer-review platform. Author writing assistance, semantic reviewer matching, plagiarism and AI-text screening, and structured AI-drafted reviews - humans always make the final call.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="/reader" class="bg-white text-slate-950 hover:bg-indigo-50 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold shadow-sm transition">Browse published articles</a>
          <% if (!currentUser) { %>
            <a href="/register" class="bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold shadow-sm transition">Create account</a>
            <a href="/login" class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold transition">Sign in</a>
          <% } else if (currentUser.role === 'author') { %>
            <a href="/author/submit" class="bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold shadow-sm transition">Submit a paper</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">A</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold mt-4 text-lg">Author writing assistant</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Polish your abstract, get AI title suggestions and keyword extraction before you hit submit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">E</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold mt-4 text-lg">Smart reviewer matching</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Cosine similarity over expertise tags plus conflict-of-interest detection. Editor keeps the final pick.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">I</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold mt-4 text-lg">Integrity screening</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Corpus similarity and stylometric AI-text signals - always a flag for review, never a verdict.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">R</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold mt-4 text-lg">AI reviewer drafts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">A structured first-pass review you can edit before submitting - every AI assist is logged.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num text-5xl text-indigo-300">5</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Role-aware dashboards</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Author, reviewer, editor, admin, reader. Each gets exactly the screen they need.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num text-5xl text-amber-300">$0</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">To run today</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Local AI by default - no API key required. Flip one env var to upgrade to Claude.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num text-5xl text-emerald-300">100%</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Audited AI calls</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Every AI assist is logged with input/output tokens. Defensible, transparent, debuggable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
